data.description: SHOWINGS BEGIN 2/24 at the OPEN HOUSE.  This end unit 3 bed/2 bath townhome features include a living room with a VAULTED CEILING a SKYLIGHT and a FIREPLACE, a dining room, kitchen, and a partially FINISHED BASEMENT. The kitchen features SHAKER cabinets, SOFT CLOSE doors and drawers, CROWN MOLDING, STAINLESS STEEL appliances, GRANITE countertops, and a PANTRY. Down the hall, you will find a full bathroom and the first bedroom with access to the backyard. Upstairs you will find another full bathroom and two bedrooms each with their own UNIQUE FEATURE. The first bedroom has a sliding GLASS DOOR overlooking the living room. Perfect for listening to the crackling of the fireplace below. The second bedroom has a BALCONY overlooking the backyard. Back downstairs past the kitchen, you will find the basement and laundry area. It is perfect for a FAMILY ROOM, or just extra space!  The roof, HVAC, plumbing and electrical were all updated in 2018, and it's MOVE IN READY!  Can't beat this location in the heart of Cherry Hill, with outstanding schools, shopping, dining, and just 20 minutes to Philly, 1 hour to the Shore!  Call today to make your appointment--you won't be disappointed!
